title: Portobello Mushrooms with Truffle Mash plus a Ricotta Crostini App & Vanilla Cheesecake Dessert
description: Whether you’re cooking for two or ordering additional servings for a group, this swoon-worthy spread is sure to leave everyone smitten! Delight your friends, family, or significant other with a sweet crostini starter while you make the rest of the meal. The main course features melt-in-your mouth portobellos coated in ground peppercorns and topped with chive-flecked butter. On the side, there’s crisp asparagus amandine and creamy mashed potatoes swirled with earthy truffle zest. Prepare for smiles all around as the evening lands with vanilla cheesecakes. Nothing says “I love you” like a five-star feast!
